{
  "texts": [
    "Deep learning methods.",
    "These methods learn the traits of normal patterns from past data in the training phase and judge whether the current metric is within the normal range in the online detection phase.",
    "Furthermore, deep learning methods can be categorized into the following families:Prediction-based.",
    "These methods aim to predict the \"normal\" value of the current metric according to the adjacent observations.",
    "If the ground truth is far from the predicted value, an anomaly alarm will be triggered."
  ]
}